We will have a 1-bedroom  apartment on the first floor available on April 20th, priced at 2,975.00 + $100.00 for carport (optional) +  $50.00 for storage (optional) with 1-year Lease Agreement. 
Please contact us for more information or to schedule virtual tour. Also, we invite you to go to liveatkirkhamheights.com to explore our community. 
Leasing Office hours: Monday through Friday, 9am till 6pm. Property address: 1555 5th Avenue, San Francisco, CA 94122.

Community amenities:
•	Picnic area with Barbecue grills; 
•	On-Site Laundry Facilities;
•	Patio Area;
•	Panoramic View of Golden Gate Bridge and Pacific Ocean;
•	Extra Basement Storage;
•	Assigned/Covered Parking;
•	24-hour emergency maintenance.
